# Vinted session cookie (required for the Vinted scraper)
# How to get it:
# 1. Go to https://www.vinted.fr and log in
# 2. Open DevTools (F12) > Network tab
# 3. Refresh the page and click any request to vinted.fr
# 4. In the "Request Headers", copy the entire "Cookie" header value
# 5. Paste it below (it's a long string)
#
# In Vercel: add this as an Environment Variable in your project settings
# Name: VINTED_COOKIE
# Value: <paste the cookie string here>
VINTED_COOKIE=
